content.content: Moonbeam currently has no traction External Link     Uniswap DAO helps Turkiye earthquake Site Feedback       Turkiye is struggling with a huge earthquake disaster.  Problem  Nearly 15,000 buildings were destroyed and around 8000 people lost their lives in the last 60 hours.  Many people have become homeless, and this is not something that will pass soon. The numbers will increase further!  This is an urgent priority process and it would be helpful to act quickly on issues such as forum discussion and temperature analysis.
